{"type":"answer","id":123954,"parentType":"question","parentId":14904,"uid":15246,"contents":"<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/qW4o5m7.gif\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/qW4o5m7.gif\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/qW4o5m7.gif\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a>可以看中英文對照的《聖經》；<br>\n裡面的句式簡單，反覆使用，方便理解基本的用法；<br>\n<b><a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/rrHwWnN.gif \" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/rrHwWnN.gif \" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/rrHwWnN.gif \" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a>字典</b> 非常重要，需要<i><b>英譯英的字典</b></i>，<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/IIBp49c.gif\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/IIBp49c.gif\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/IIBp49c.gif\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a>儘量不要中文翻譯，看到一個單詞，只聯想到英文，讓思維不受中文影響；<br>\n舉例：<br>\nLEARN<br>\nDefinition of&nbsp;<i>learn :to gain knowledge or understanding of or skill in by study, instruction, or experience</i><br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/uzDqFVl.gif\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/uzDqFVl.gif\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/uzDqFVl.gif\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a>最重要的是要能說，口音不重要，說出的每一句都是你掌握的；<br>\n不要想著在腦子裡做翻譯以後說出來，而是不用想，<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/wlSgwLm.gif\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/wlSgwLm.gif\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/wlSgwLm.gif\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a>脫口而出，是最高境界<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/NVmcfxg.gif\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/NVmcfxg.gif\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/NVmcfxg.gif\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a>;<br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/BRLpBYR.gif\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/BRLpBYR.gif\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/BRLpBYR.gif\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a>樓主加油！","date":"2020-01-08","agreeCount":6,"discussionCount":0}